        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>State and National Guard Fairness Act of 2020</b></p> <p>This bill allows a miscellaneous itemized deduction for unreimbursed expenses incurred by members of an Armed Forces reserve component or state defense forces.</p>]]></text>
